title: We're growing! And we want to meet awesome new people.
content: If you don't feel like reading, just come by for a coffee instead, we are located at Holtermansgatan 1c, Gothenburg.
contact: Contact us at team@equilab.horse and let us talk it over! We are based in Gothenburg.

data.the_task: We at Equilab are right now looking for at least two new developers. We are a small team so if you are intrested there is a good possibility to do more than app development. For exemple som ebackend (python and node), design or even play around with our machine learing.
data.description: Breaking Things, Curious, Swift, Java (testing Kotlin), Firebase, Realm, Fastlane, A/B testing, Sketchapp, Slack and Trello.

data.the_task: For each that pass we have a growing amount of information to process and your task will be to help us gain from this data. We are a small team so if you are intrested there is a good possibility to do more than Pattern Recogniction/DevOps development.
